    "summary": "Globally experienced executive experienced achieving growth targets, rebuilding teams and setting new Strategies with hands on mentality.  \n*Spend the last 13 months on rebuilding the China team new China Strategy. At the same time delivered strong double digits growth in Singapore.\n*Pushed the envelop with the Korean business from $87M to $148M in less than two years.  Key competencies include: corporate development, building organizations, managing matrix complexity, customer relationships, and regulatory issues.   Ideal role would be with an enterprise committed to international growth and capital intensity that requires a leader who can balance revenue generation, cost management, organizational development, strategic thinking and both mature and emerging market development.\n\nACHIEVEMENTS\n\n\u2022\tRebuild China team and co-developed new China Strategy\n\u2022\tTurned over the Indirect versus Direct business in Korea from 40:60 into a more profitable 70:30. \n\u2022\tEstablished a fully functional Shared Service Center with IT, HR, Legal, Supply chain and Finance in India within two years.\n\u2022\tCreated a strategic plan for the India organization with clear commercial and organizational goals.\n\u2022\tSuccessful triple product introductions throughout Europe from the FTIR/Raman Product line.\n\u2022\tIntegrated two business units into a newly formed division within the Benelux organization\n\u2022\tAs Country Commercial Leader strived towards one face to the customer for all divisions and business units in Benelux",
